'''新加坡理工大學'''（{{lang-en|Singapore Institute of Technology}}，縮寫：{{lang|en|SIT}}）是一座[[新加坡|新加坡]]的[[自治大學|自治大學]]，成立於2009年。

[[新加坡國會|新加坡國會]]在2014年2月17日通過一項議案，准許該大學頒發自己的學位證書，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.gov.sg/sites/default/files/Singapore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Bill%207-2014.pdf|title=Singapore Institute of Technology Bill|publisher=parliament.gov.sg|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307195603/http://www.parliament.gov.sg/sites/default/files/Singapore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Bill%207-2014.pdf|archivedate=2014-03-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.moe.gov.sg/media/parliamentary-replies/2014/02/second-reading-speech-on-the-singapore-institute-of-technology-bill.php |title=Second Reading Speech on the Singapore Institute of Technology Bill |publisher=moe.gov.sg |accessdate=2014-04-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309162535/http://www.moe.gov.sg/media/parliamentary-replies/2014/02/second-reading-speech-on-the-singapore-institute-of-technology-bill.php |archivedate=2014-03-09 }}</ref>此議案在當年生效。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.asiaone.com/news/edvantage/sit-becomes-5th-autonomous-uni-here|title=SIT Becomes Fifth Autonomous University|publisher=asiaone.com|access-date=2015-02-02|archive-date=2019-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126000730/http://news.asiaone.com/news/edvantage/sit-becomes-5th-autonomous-uni-here|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

現時新加坡理工大學除了位置於[[杜佛|杜佛]]的臨時校園外, 學生需於國內五所理工學院上課。

2015年[[新加坡總理|新加坡總理]][[李顯龍|李顯龍]]於當年的國慶群眾大會宣布將於[[榜鵝|榜鵝]]預留土地興建新加坡理工大學新的永久校園。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/national-day-rally-2015-singapore-institute-of-technologys-new-central-campus-to-be-housed|title=National Day Rally 2015: Singapore Institute of Technology's new central campus to be housed in Punggol|publisher=Strait Times|4=|archivedate=2020-11-08|accessdate=2019-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108170905/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/national-day-rally-2015-singapore-institute-of-technologys-new-central-campus-to-be-housed|dead-url=no}}</ref>新校園建築工程於[[2019年|2019年]][[9月10日|9月10日]]正式動工, 新校園預計於[[2023年|2023年]]落成。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.singaporetech.edu.sg/digitalnewsroom/a-smart-campus-to-call-home--sit-begins-construction-of-centralised-campus-in-punggol-with-groundbreaking-ceremony/|title=A SMART CAMPUS TO CALL HOME – SIT BEGINS CONSTRUCTION OF CENTRALISED CAMPUS IN PUNGGOL WITH GROUNDBREAKING CEREMONY|publisher=Singapore Institute of Technology|4=|accessdate=2019-09-10|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020112817/https://www.singaporetech.edu.sg/digitalnewsroom/a-smart-campus-to-call-home--sit-begins-construction-of-centralised-campus-in-punggol-with-groundbreaking-ceremony/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

